  TTestMediator (TTestComponent)
    +--- TTestMediatorA (TComponentA)
    |      +--- TTestMediatorC (TComponentC)
    +--- TTestMediatorB (TComponentB)
    |      +--- TTestMediatorD (TComponentD)
    +--- TTestMediatorE (TComponentE)
    +--- TTestMediatorComposite (TComponentA)
